"{\n  \"text\": \"Hi everybody. What's all the hubbub about living foods? Why am I constantly going on about this? Why not just take a pill? What's what's wrong with the probiotic? Well, in my opinion, a probiotic is not nearly as effective as foods because it is not nearly as biodiverse. A probiotic pill is one or two or maybe a half dozen strains of bacteria that have been cultivated in a petri dish. And it's the same bacteria done trillions and trillions or however many times, and it's not trillions of different types of bacteria, which is what you really need. Because you have to regrow your bacteria and you have to do that by sharing it or giving it tools. And you don't know which tools are the ones that it's going to need. And this is constantly changing anyway. So even if you did know, it would be different in the next five minutes. So what you need to do is give it a diverse set of tools. And that's what probiotics lack is diversity. Anyway, thanks, y'all.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" Hi everybody.\",\n      \"start\": 0.96,\n      \"end\": 2.16,\n      \"duration\": 1.2,\n      \"confidence\": 0.981,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" Hi\",\n          \"start\": 0.96,\n          \"end\": 1.28,\n          \"duration\": 0.32,\n          \"confidence\": 0.997\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" ever\",\n          \"start\": 1.52,\n          \"end\": 1.68,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"yb\",\n          \"start\": 1.68,\n          \"end\": 1.84,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"ody\",\n          \"start\": 1.84,\n          \"end\": 2.0,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \".\",\n          \"start\": 2.0,\n          \"end\": 2.16,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 0.9